# Stage explanation in simple words

## Clone

Jenkins downloads project from GitHub.

## Build Image

Jenkins creates Docker image from Dockerfile.

## Push to Docker Hub

Jenkins uploads image to Docker Hub.

## Deploy

Jenkins runs the containerized application.

